Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:36.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:01.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:38.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! Where the hell were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who took off without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know where\NYuzu and Karin are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they're back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:55.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:56.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you? Where were you\Nlooking all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good, now I can go look for Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of my kid sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:06.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! If I knew they'd make us\Nhelp clean up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:16.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have come to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of lecturing us,\Nmake the ones responsible do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you made such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:25.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But all of them were\Nacting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's Hime doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hime! If you stand there looking\Nso cute and spaced out…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you blurting out\Nall of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What?\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:52.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm… There's a TV show\NI want to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so let's call it a day and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:55.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry. Tatsuki, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please…hurry! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing I thought was,\N"I wish I didn't notice."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I thought,\N"We have to get away from here."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One thing I know for sure…\Nthat thing is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:23.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Every cell in my body is tingling,\Ntrying to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t create a panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and keep looking calm as\N though nothing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:39.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to change,\Nso you two go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, it disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki, um…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,20...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, this is for you, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Hime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please run, Chizuru! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!\NNot the windows again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hime, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:28.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?! Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oweee…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:36.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shedding tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So cute…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:46.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I don't know what happened,\Nbut I seem to be fine. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Though I do\Nlike your crying face…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer your smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NC-Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!\NMy hand is acting on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why's this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Chizuru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hime?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:26.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I just used\Na little of my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:35.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I use these seeds\Nfrom my forehead to take control of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:39.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And make you humans\N fight amongst yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:41.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone, let us start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice it earlier.\NThat thing over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you can see it, too, Tatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:27.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where the thing that made you cry is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you big blob over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:33.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You picked a fight with\Nthe wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been this way for a long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that anyone who makes\NOrihime cry, will get it from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:45.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:52.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You're all such wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Tatsuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something’s happened to me…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:26.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The seed I shot into you will soon\Ntake root and control your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:31.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nyour body is mine to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Do you realize the position\Nyou're in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have almost\Nno control of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? How's that? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:08:59.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:18.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Orihime…don't cry, Ori…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, you have such pretty hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice, warm color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a show-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cut your hair, Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you spacing out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of you that\NI was able to grow my hair long again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never cut my hair short again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:35.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because this long hair\Nis proof of my trust in you, Tatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:40.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…\Nfor protecting me until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So please…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ori…hime…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki, this time, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki said, "You picked a fight\Nwith the wrong person."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You picked the wrong person\Nto hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will not forgive anyone\Nwho hurts Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Using strange powers…\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:50.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:57.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, she noticed us…\Nthat we exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:58.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:03.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we've always been\N the closest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello…Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Shunshun Rikka—\NThe Six Princess-Shielding Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:20.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were born in order\Nto protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We are your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fairies! Airborne fairies\Nare talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:35.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cute reaction.\NBut we're not fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we are the powers\Ninside your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We are a part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore,\Nonly you can see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:48.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, although… people like\NIchigo Kurosaki can probably see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's because of him\Nthat we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:05.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to understand\Nwho we are or where we came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You seem so arrogant…\Neven though you're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! In any case,\Nlearn how to use us right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:13.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Use?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our power can put up\Na "shield" to reject.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to activate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you must use your "heart" and\Nyour "Kotodama – Spirit Chant."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kotodama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:27.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What've you been mumbling\Nabout over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Orihime!\NCall our names!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Baigon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must summon them\Nwith your Kotodama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku, Baigon, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku, Baigon, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santen Kesshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santen Kesshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:12.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their power rejects what\Nis "outside the shield."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They put up a shield between\Nyou and your enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:21.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and reject any attacks\Ndirected at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:25.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,our power is to reject\Nwhat is "within the shield."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We make a limited space\N with our shield
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and we can reverse any damage\Nthat has been inflicted inside the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now say our names.\N I am Shuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shuno, Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then recite the Kotodama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soten Kishun! I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:58.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Woman! There's no time for tears!\NI'm up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My power is to reject what is on\Neither side of the shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I put up a shield inside the enemy,\Nand reject his material bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\NI can cut the enemy in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now say it!\NMy name is Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Koten Zanshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Orihime!\N– Orihime...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear… I guess using all of us\Nso soon was too much for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:48.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But, Orihime really did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! The man's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:28.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure of it. The man was\Nbeaten up and lying here…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a liar!\NHe really WAS hurt and…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say no more, Karin.\N Father understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:44.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so busy lately,\Nand have had no time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:49.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That you would go so far as to lie\Nto get attention from your father…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now Karin…\Njump into my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come hug me as hard\Nas you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:04.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place gives me a weird feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So all's well here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're up? Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um…where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're up at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But…it seems\Nwe were saved by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:44.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Now then,\Nwhere to begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going to\Nmake him cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not able to kill in\None shot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:09.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There're far too many for\N that small amount of bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:13.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though they were lured\Nby an even greater force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I swear I will avenge\Nyour death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Path of Destruction Four:\NByaku Rai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:32.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:36.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These Hollows are small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even beat these Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,does it mean my powers\Nhaven't returned at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How I longed to see you, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kon, aren’t you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good to get\Nkicked like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:06.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're in Ichigo's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that means he transformed\Ninto a Soul Reaper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err… Sis, behind you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:21.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good, you seem okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:27.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki. It's my first time\Nspeaking to you face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Totally ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now. So this is your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely. This is a battle between\Nme and the Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:43.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't let anyone in town die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:46.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Ichigo Kurosaki is defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will give my life to protect\Nthe people of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He, the Soul Reaper,\Nwill watch me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:56.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as I protect everything and\Neveryone from the Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:58.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I cannot do that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,this battle is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:19.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, all this about Soul Reapers\Nand Hollows…it's so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:23.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you deny the fact\Nthat you were attacked earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki is fighting Hollows\Nas a Soul Reaper as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the strong spiritual energy that\Nhe released has influenced you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's all up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,whether you open the gate that\Nhas appeared before you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Ridge has begun to converge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:56.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:06.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you…\Nwhat is beyond the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I found you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:04.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:09.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:14.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:19.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:29.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:33.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:40.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:43.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time for Isshin Kurosaki's\NFatherly Love 101!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, all together...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:46.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A father's love is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A father's love will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A father's love is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:50.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A father's love is-!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you,\Nthis is a preview!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:55.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode...is great.